### 获取所有成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/scores
Accept: application/json

### 创建新成绩
POST http://localhost:8080/api/scores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "courseId": 1,
  "examType": "FINAL",
  "score": 85.5,
  "semester": "2025-SPRING"
}

### 创建新成绩（不及格）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/scores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "courseId": 2,
  "examType": "FINAL",
  "score": 55,
  "semester": "2025-SPRING"
}

### 更新成绩
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/scores/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "courseId": 1,
  "examType": "FINAL",
  "score": 92,
  "semester": "2025-SPRING"
}

### 获取特定成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/scores/1
Accept: application/json

### 获取学生所有成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/scores/student/1
Accept: application/json

### 获取特定学期所有成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/scores/semester/2025-SPRING
Accept: application/json

### 获取学生在特定学期的成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/scores/student/1/semester/2025-SPRING
Accept: application/json

### 获取学生在特定学期的平均成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/scores/student/1/semester/2025-SPRING/average
Accept: application/json

### 获取课程在特定学期的平均成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/scores/course/1/semester/2025-SPRING/average
Accept: application/json

### 删除成绩
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/scores/1
Accept: application/json

### 批量删除成绩
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/scores/batch
Content-Type: application/json

[1, 2, 3]

